ed="T" n="0869b16"/><persName key="A011803">釋惟恭</persName>，不詳何許人也。少孺出俗于<placeName key="PL000000027760">法性<lb
ed="T" n="0869b17"/>寺</placeName>，好尚偪下<ptr target="#n3116"/>，多狎非<anchor xml:id="beg0869004"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>法</sic><corr>益</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0869004"/>之友。雖乖僧行，<lb
ed="T" n="0869b18"/>猶勤持誦《金剛般若》<ptr target="#n3066"/>，罕離脣齒。酒徒博侶，<lb
ed="T" n="0869b19"/>交集門庭，虛誑云為，曾無廉恥。後遇病且<lb
ed="T" n="0869b20"/>死<ptr target="#n3115"/>。<ref type="place" target="#PL000000027760">同寺</ref>有<persName key="A013600">靈巋</persName>，其跡相類，號為一寺二害<lb
ed="T" n="0869b21"/>也。<persName key="A013600">巋</persName>偶出，去<ref type="place" target="#PL000000027760">寺</ref>一里所，逢六七人<ptr target="#n695"/>少年甚<lb
ed="T" n="0869b22"/>都，衣服鮮潔，各執樂器如龜茲部<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2177"/>，問<persName key="A013600">靈巋</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0869b23"/>曰：「<persName key="A011803">惟恭</persName>上人何在？」<persName key="A013600">巋</persName>即語其處，疑<ref type="place" target="#PL000000027760">其寺</ref>行<lb
ed="T" n="0869b24"/>香<ptr type="glossary" target="#g594"/>樂佛也。及曉，迴入<ref type="place" target="#PL000000027760">寺</ref>，聞鐘聲，云「<persName key="A011803">恭</persName>卒」<ptr target="#n696"/>。<lb
ed="T" n="0869b25"/>所見者乃天樂耳。蓋承經力，必生淨剎<ptr target="#n697"/>，亦<lb
ed="T" n="0869b26"/>以其跡勉<persName key="A013600">靈巋</persName>也。<persName key="A013600">巋</persName>感悟折節<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2024"/>，緇門崇重，<lb
ed="T" n="0869b27"/>終成高邁焉。</p>
